text: Nadine Kunz (born 11 November 1983) is a German water polo player. She was part of the German women's national water polo team at the 2001 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2006 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2007 World Aquatics Championships, and 2009 FINA Women's World Championships. == References == == Other websites == * https://rfen.es/es/posts/news/219223 * https://www.zimbio.com/photos/Nadine+Kunz category:1983 births Category:Living people category:German water polo players
